    "            continue #THIS IS BEING DONE SO THAT IF THE PLAYER TYPE SOMETHING OTHER THAN 'HIT' OR 'STAND', THE GAME WILL ASK THE PLAYER AGAIN FOR IT'S CHOICE. IT WILL CONTINUE ASKING THE CHOICE OF THE PLAYER UNTIL IT PROVIDE THE CORRECT INPUT.\n",
    "        \n",
    "        break"
